summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Forward Thrust Park Plan and Program; making determinations pursuant to Sections 5 and 6 of King County Resolution 34571 that certain projects therein are impractical to substantially accomplish; authorizing allocation of moneys thereby made available to be applied to other projects authorized by said Resolution 34571 or additional projects which may be declared by the Legislative Authorities of the City and County to be consistent with said Resolution and a County purposes, or other projects which may be authorized by the Qualified electors of King County.
